{"id":24440986607,"name":"Test","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAFsMvb7w","head_branch":"DHIS2-21287-41","head_sha":"e0425ecd670839cf48b8305e91cd657197998a1d","path":".github/workflows/run-tests.yml","run_number":52593,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"perf: replace linear scans with indexed lookups in tracker import DHIS2-21287 [41]","status":"completed","conclusion":"success","workflow_id":10954,"check_suite_id":64686684449,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAAPD6B5IQ","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24440986607","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24440986607","created_at":"2026-04-15T07:00:26Z","updated_at":"2026-04-15T07:18:31Z","run_started_at":"2026-04-15T07:00:26Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24440986607/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24440986607/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/64686684449","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24440986607/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24440986607/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/24440986607/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"perf: replace linear scans with indexed lookups in tracker import DHIS2-21287 (#23590)\n\n* perf: replace linear stream scans with Map lookups in tracker import\n\nTrackerBundle.findById does a linear stream scan on every call, invoked\n6+ times per enrollment from different validators. With 500 TEs per\nrequest this means ~3,000 linear scans. Replace with lazily-built\nMap\u003cUID, T\u003e indexes that are invalidated when lists change.\n\nAlso replace the linear TE scan in UniqueAttributesSupplier\ngetEntityForEnrollment with a pre-built Map lookup.\n\nDHIS2-21287\n\n* perf: cache mandatory attribute sets in TrackerPreheat\n\nvalidateRequiredProperties and validateMandatoryAttributes rebuild the\nset of mandatory program/TE-type attributes per entity via stream scans\nof program.getProgramAttributes() and trackedEntityType\n.getTrackedEntityTypeAttributes(). With 500 TEs and 20 attributes per\nrequest, this causes thousands of redundant stream operations.\n\nCache the mandatory attribute sets lazily in TrackerPreheat keyed by\nprogram/TE-type UID. The set is computed once on first access and reused\nfor all entities of the same program/type.\n\nDHIS2-21287\n\n* chore: remove unnecessary transient and JsonIgnore from TrackerBundle\n\nTrackerBundle does not implement Serializable so transient has no\neffect. The private getter methods prevent Lombok from generating\npublic getters, so Jackson will not see these fields and JsonIgnore\nis also unnecessary.\n\nDHIS2-21287","author":{"name":"teleivo","email":"teleivo@users.noreply.github.com"},"id":"e0425ecd670839cf48b8305e91cd657197998a1d","tree_id":"a1ade9f974823dfc543c29559be1d6b7bc7ac982","timestamp":"2026-04-15T06:58:27Z","committer":{"name":"teleivo","email":"teleivo@users.noreply.github.com"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://ap